{"messages":[{"role":"agent","type":"taskBlock","taskTitle":"Création du composant UnifiedTask","taskStatus":"content_copy","taskSummary":"Tous les fichiers (manager, server, ui) sont modifiés pour gérer l'historisation des \"TaskBlocks\". Le rendu\nui.js\naffiche désormais une seule bulle par tâche, qui contient la frise complète des statuts numérotés accompagnés de leurs paragraphes respectifs. Je redémarre le serveur pour valider ce comportement.","html":"<div class=\"flex flex-col\"><span class=\"font-semibold text-ide-text-color\">Création du composant UnifiedTask</span><div class=\"text-sm\"><div class=\"leading-relaxed select-text text-sm flex flex-col [&amp;_code:not(pre_code)]:bg-code-background [&amp;_code:not(pre_code)]:text-code-foreground [&amp;_code:not(pre_code)]:rounded [&amp;_code:not(pre_code)]:px-1 [&amp;_code:not(pre_code)]:py-0.5 [&amp;_code:not(pre_code)]:text-[0.9em] [&amp;_summary]:cursor-pointer [&amp;_h1]:text-xl [&amp;_h2]:text-lg [&amp;_h3]:text-base [&amp;_h4]:text-sm [&amp;_h1]:font-semibold [&amp;_h2]:font-semibold [&amp;_h3]:font-medium [&amp;_h4]:font-medium [&amp;_h1]:!mb-2 [&amp;_h1]:!mt-3 [&amp;_h2]:!mb-2 [&amp;_h2]:!mt-3 [&amp;_h3]:!mb-1 [&amp;_h3]:!mt-2 [&amp;_h4]:!mb-1 [&amp;_h4]:!mt-2 [&amp;_li.task-list-item]:list-none [&amp;_ul:has(li.task-list-item)]:list-none [&amp;_ul]:my-2 [&amp;_ol]:my-2 [&amp;&gt;ul.contains-task-list]:pl-0 [&amp;&gt;ol.contains-task-list]:pl-0 [&amp;_ul]:pl-10 [&amp;_ol]:pl-10 [&amp;&gt;ul:not(.contains-task-list)]:!pl-4 [&amp;&gt;ol:not(.contains-task-list)]:!pl-4 [&amp;_ul]:list-disc [&amp;_ol]:list-decimal [&amp;_li.task-checked&gt;.task-checked-content]:opacity-50 break-words text-ide-text-color prose-a:text-ide-link-color gap-2\"><p node=\"[object Object]\">Tous les fichiers (manager, server, ui) sont modifiés pour gérer l'historisation des \"TaskBlocks\". Le rendu <span class=\"context-scope-mention\"><span class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-0.5 rounded-md align-middle text-sm font-medium transition-[opacity,background-color] cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-500/20 select-text translate-y-[-1px]\" draggable=\"true\" style=\"padding: 1px 0.25rem 1px 0.125rem;\"><div><img src=\"http://localhost:9000/c:/Users/Jamet/AppData/Local/Programs/Antigravity/resources/app/extensions/theme-symbols/src/icons/files/js.svg\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" style=\"min-width: 16px; display: inline-block; min-height: 16px; transform: translateY(-1px);\"></div><span class=\"inline-flex break-all leading-tight\">ui.js</span></span></span> affiche désormais une seule bulle par tâche, qui contient la frise complète des statuts numérotés accompagnés de leurs paragraphes respectifs. Je redémarre le serveur pour valider ce comportement.</p></div></div></div>"},{"role":"agent","type":"taskBlock","taskTitle":"Refining Operational Protocols","taskStatus":"","taskSummary":"I've been meticulously refining my operational protocols. I'm actively avoiding the use of 'cat' for file creation or appending, opting for more secure and efficient methods. I'm prioritizing grep_search over grep within Bash commands, and steering clear of 'ls' and 'cat' for simple listing and viewing tasks. The goal is to optimize and reinforce security.","html":"<div class=\"pl-6 overflow-y-auto max-h-[200px] relative\"><div><div class=\"leading-relaxed select-text text-sm flex flex-col [&amp;_code:not(pre_code)]:bg-code-background [&amp;_code:not(pre_code)]:text-code-foreground [&amp;_code:not(pre_code)]:rounded [&amp;_code:not(pre_code)]:px-1 [&amp;_code:not(pre_code)]:py-0.5 [&amp;_code:not(pre_code)]:text-[0.9em] [&amp;_summary]:cursor-pointer [&amp;_h1]:text-xl [&amp;_h2]:text-lg [&amp;_h3]:text-base [&amp;_h4]:text-sm [&amp;_h1]:font-semibold [&amp;_h2]:font-semibold [&amp;_h3]:font-medium [&amp;_h4]:font-medium [&amp;_h1]:!mb-2 [&amp;_h1]:!mt-3 [&amp;_h2]:!mb-2 [&amp;_h2]:!mt-3 [&amp;_h3]:!mb-1 [&amp;_h3]:!mt-2 [&amp;_h4]:!mb-1 [&amp;_h4]:!mt-2 [&amp;_li.task-list-item]:list-none [&amp;_ul:has(li.task-list-item)]:list-none [&amp;_ul]:my-2 [&amp;_ol]:my-2 [&amp;&gt;ul.contains-task-list]:pl-0 [&amp;&gt;ol.contains-task-list]:pl-0 [&amp;_ul]:pl-10 [&amp;_ol]:pl-10 [&amp;&gt;ul:not(.contains-task-list)]:!pl-4 [&amp;&gt;ol:not(.contains-task-list)]:!pl-4 [&amp;_ul]:list-disc [&amp;_ol]:list-decimal [&amp;_li.task-checked&gt;.task-checked-content]:opacity-50 break-words [&amp;_strong]:block [&amp;_strong]:my-2 opacity-70 gap-2\"><p node=\"[object Object]\"><p class=\"!mb-0 mt-0 animate-markdown\"><strong>Refining Operational Protocols</strong></p></p>\n<p node=\"[object Object]\"><p class=\"!mb-0 mt-0 animate-markdown\"><span>I've </span><span>been </span><span>meticulously </span><span>refining </span><span>my </span><span>operational </span><span>protocols. </span><span>I'm </span><span>actively </span><span>avoiding </span><span>the </span><span>use </span><span>of </span><span>'cat' </span><span>for </span><span>file </span><span>creation </span><span>or </span><span>appending, </span><span>opting </span><span>for </span><span>more </span><span>secure </span><span>and </span><span>efficient </span><span>methods. </span><span>I'm </span><span>prioritizing </span><span></span><code node=\"[object Object]\" class=\"whitespace-pre-wrap\" style=\"word-break: break-word;\">grep_search</code><span> </span><span>over </span><span></span><code node=\"[object Object]\" class=\"whitespace-pre-wrap\" style=\"word-break: break-word;\">grep</code><span> </span><span>within </span><span>Bash </span><span>commands, </span><span>and </span><span>steering </span><span>clear </span><span>of </span><span>'ls' </span><span>and </span><span>'cat' </span><span>for </span><span>simple </span><span>listing </span><span>and </span><span>viewing </span><span>tasks. </span><span>The </span><span>goal </span><span>is </span><span>to </span><span>optimize </span><span>and </span><span>reinforce </span><span>security.</span></p></p></div></div></div><div class=\"absolute left-0 right-4 top-0 h-4 bg-gradient-to-b from-ide-task-section-background to-transparent pointer-events-none\"></div>"}],"isFull":false,"isStreaming":true,"scrollInfo":{"scrollTop":255492.34375,"scrollHeight":256306,"clientHeight":414}}